      "date": "2012-07-27 00:00:37.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nAndreas, the comment in the patch actually refers to the osd-using-mdd issues, not mdd-using-ldiskfs.  We need a Jira ticket to track the work required to remove such dependency after LOD/OSP is landed.  See also http://git.whamcloud.com/?p=fs/lustre-release.git;a=commit;h=c69f7adac0f87a4c31706b62bd72c780d2563586.  I'll ask Johann to fill more details into a new ticket.",
